FAQs
----

*   How do I sign up?
    
    When you sign up for an account, you can choose between the 'Free', 'Pro' or 'Team' plan. If you'd like to change or upgrade your plan later, click 'Products' in the left sidebar of the Setmore app. You'll get the option to select the plan you'd like.
    
*   When do I make a payment?
    
    Your billing cycle for a 'Pro' or 'Team' account begins the day you sign up. Your subscription will automatically renew based on the billing period (monthly/annual) you choose.
    
*   Can I cancel my subscription?
    
    You can cancel your subscription at any time. You can try 'Pro' or 'Team' risk-free for 30 days and if you're not satisfied, contact us to request a refund.
    
*   How do I make a payment?
    
    We accept all major debit and credit cards online. You can update your billing information in your Setmore account at any time.
    
*   What does 'user' mean?
    
    Setmore charges per 'user' or by each staff member with their own profile. Each staff calendar counts as a user even if the owner/assignee does not have login permission.
    

For more information, explore our [features](https://www.setmore.com/features), [integrations](https://www.setmore.com/integrations), and [use cases](https://www.setmore.com/industries).
